description: Arnott’s Shapes Original Barbecue are an Aussie favourite savoury biscuit snack with a rich tomato flavour and loads of herbs on a salty, crispy cracker base. Oven baked, not fried, and foil-wrapped for freshness.Arnott’s Shapes Originals are big on crunch and even bigger on taste – and perfect for any occasion! These savoury biscuits are delicious oven-baked crackers with loads of flavour you can see, and no artificial colours or preservatives. Whether you’re sharing with friends at the park or looking for a fun afternoon snack with flavours that your whole family will love, Arnott’s Shapes Original Barbecue biscuits are the perfect flavoured cracker. Foil-wrapped for freshness, they’re a go-to savoury cravings-buster for any occasion. Bags of flavour in every box, no matter which flavour you savour!A rich tomato flavour with loads of herbs on a salty, crispy cracker base.Flavour you can see.Foil-wrapped for freshness.Oven baked, not fried.Made in Australia.
